[SN]TITLE[SN]
Josh Thompson: Macclesfield Town sign ex-Celtic defender

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
National League club Macclesfield Town have signed former Celtic, Colchester and Tranmere defender Josh Thompson on a free transfer.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Thompson was captain of relegated Southport last season scoring one goal in 26 appearances.
The 26-year-old has not played a competitive fixture since seriously injuring his patella in January.
A former England Under-19 international, Thompson is the Silkmen's eighth signing of the summer.
